This program was created for the following purposes:
[ * ] Encrypting sensitive information
[ * ] Passing information in unreadable formats
[ * ] P2P encrypted messaging

This program have the following abilities:
[ * ] Encode text to binary
[ * ] Encode text to hexadecimal 
[ * ] Encode text to octa-deximal
[ * ] Encode text to decimal

[ * ] Decode binary to text
[ * ] Decode hexadecimal to text
[ * ] Decode octa-decimal to text
[ * ] Decode decimal to text

Note: This program was created for security purposes only. The programmer will not be accountable for damages caused with the program.